 in Leipzig: Hasenh\u00fcttl und RB gehen getrennte Wege |website=kicker.de |publisher=[[Kicker (sports magazine)|kicker]] |date=16 May 2018 |access-date=16 May 2018 |language=German}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kicker.de/news/fussball/bundesliga/startseite/727195/artikel_rangnick-wieder-chef---auch-wegen-des-themas-sprache.html |title=Rangnick wieder Chef \u2013 auch \"wegen des Themas Sprache\" |website=kicker.de |publisher=[[Kicker (sports magazine)|kicker]] |date=9 July 2018 |access-date=9 July 2018 |language=German}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"left\" | [[VfB Stuttgart]]\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|TUR}} [[Tayfun Korkut]]\n| rowspan=\"7\"|Sacked\n| colspan=\"2\"|7 October 2018\n| 18th\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|GER}} [[Markus Weinzierl]]\n| colspan=\"2\"|9 October 2018\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.vfb.de/de/vfb/aktuell/neues/profis/2018/vfb-stellt-tayfun-korkut-frei/|title=VfB Stuttgart stellt Cheftrainer Tayfun Korkut frei|website=vfb.de |publisher=[[VfB Stuttgart]] |date=7 October 2018 |access-date=7 October 2018 |language=German}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.vfb.de/de/vfb/aktuell/neues/profis/2018/meldung-trainer/|title=Markus Weinzierl ist neuer Cheftrainer des VfB|website=vfb.de |publisher=[[VfB Stuttgart]] |date=9 October 2018 |access-date=9 October 2018 |language=German}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"left\" | [[Bayer 04 Leverkusen|Bayer Leverkusen]]\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|GER}} [[Heiko Herrlich]]\n| colspan=\"2\"|23 December 2018\n| 9th\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|NED}} [[Peter Bosz]]\n| colspan=\"2\"|23 December 2018\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bayer04.de/de-de/news/bayer04/peter-bosz-uebernimmt-trainer-amt-von-heiko-herrlich/|title= Peter Bosz \u00fcbernimmt Trainer-Amt von Heiko Herrlich |website=bayer04.de |publisher=[[Bayer 04 Leverkusen]] |date=23 December 2018 |access-date=23 December 2018 |language=German}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"left\" | [[Hannover 96]]\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|GER}} [[Andr\u00e9 Breiten