na D\u00fcsseldorf]]\n|-\n| align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|GER}} [[Alexander Schwolow]]\n| align=\"left\"|[[SC Freiburg]]\n|}\n\n==Number of teams by state==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Position\n![[States of Germany|State]]\n!Number\n!Teams\n|-\n|align=center|1\n|{{flag|North Rhine-Westphalia}}||align=center|5||align=center|[[Borussia Dortmund]], [[Fortuna D\u00fcsseldorf]], [[Bayer 04 Leverkusen|Bayer Leverkusen]], [[Borussia M\u00f6nchengladbach]] and [[FC Schalke 04|Schalke 04]]\n|-\n|align=center rowspan=\"2\"|2\n|{{flag|Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg}}||align=center|3||align=center|[[SC Freiburg]], [[TSG 1899 Hoffenheim|1899 Hoffenheim]] and [[VfB Stuttgart]]\n|-\n|{{flag|Bavaria}}||align=center|3||align=center|[[FC Augsburg]], [[FC Bayern Munich|Bayern Munich]] and [[1. FC N\u00fcrnberg]]\n|-\n|align=center|4\n|{{flag|Lower Saxony}}||align=center|2||align=center|[[Hannover 96]] and [[VfL Wolfsburg]]\n|-\n|align=center rowspan=\"5\"|5\n|{{flag|Berlin}}||align=center|1||align=center|[[Hertha BSC]]\n|-\n|{{flag|Bremen}}||align=center|1||align=center|[[SV Werder Bremen|Werder Bremen]]\n|-\n|{{flag|Hesse}}||align=center|1||align=center|[[Eintracht Frankfurt]]\n|-\n|{{flag|Rhineland-Palatinate}}||align=center|1||align=center|[[1. FSV Mainz 05|Mainz 05]]\n|-\n|{{flag|Saxony}}||align=center|1||align=center|[[RB Leipzig]]\n|}\n\n==Monthly awards==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Month\n! colspan=\"2\" | Player of the Month\n! colspan=\"2\" | Rookie of the Month\n! colspan=\"2\" | Goal of the Month\n! rowspan=\"2\" | {{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n! Player\n! Club\n! Player\n! Club\n! Player\n! Club\n|-\n! August\n| colspan=\"2\" {{N/a}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{N/a}}\n| {{flagicon|BEL}} [[Axel Witsel]]\n| [[Borussia Dortmund]]\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | <ref name=\"bundesliga_19-2583-803\">{{cite news |title=Bundesliga's March Player of the Month nominees |publisher=Bundesliga |url=https://www.bundesliga.com/en/bundesliga/news/player-of-the-month-2018-19-ea-sports-fifa-19-2583-803 |date=17 May 2019 |accessdate=17 May 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"rookie-award_2018-19\">{{cite news |title=BUNDESLIGA ROOKIE AWARD 2018/19 presented by TAG Heuer|publisher=Bundesliga|url=https://www.rookie-award.com/en/|accessdate=17 May 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"bundesliga_2747-1210\">{{cite news |title=Vote for March's Goal of the Month |publisher=Bundesliga |url=https://www.bundesliga.com/en/bundesliga/news/goal-of-the-month-2018-19-bayern-munich-borussia-dortmund-schalke-rb-leipzig-2747-1210|date=11 April 2019 |accessdate=17 May 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! September\n| {{flagicon|GER}} [[Marco Reus]]\n| Borussia Dortmund\n| {{flagicon|MAR}} [[Achraf Hakimi]]\n| Borussia Dortmund\n| {{flagicon|DEN}} [[Jacob Bruun Larsen]]\n| Borussia Dortmund\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | <ref name=\"bundesliga_19-2583-803\"/><ref name=\"rookie-award_2018-19\"/><ref name=\"bundesliga_2747-1210\"/>\n|-\n! October\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jadon Sancho]]\n| Borussia Dortmund\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Reiss Nelson]]\n| [[TSG 1899 Hoffenheim|1899 Hoffenheim]]\n| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Paco Alc\u00e1cer]]\n| Borussia Dortmund\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | <ref name=\"bundesliga_19-2583-803\"/><ref name=\"rookie-award_2018-19\"/><ref name=\"bundesliga_2747-1210\"/>\n|-\n! November\n| rowspan=\"2\" | {{flagicon|GER}} Marco Reus\n| rowspan=\"2\" | Borussia Dortmund\n| {{flagicon|MAR}} Achraf Hakimi\n| Borussia Dortmund\n| {{flagicon|GER}} Marco Reus\n| Borussia Dortmund\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | <ref name=\"bundesliga_19-2583-803\"/><ref name=\"rookie-award_2018-19\"/><ref name=\"bundesliga_2747-1210\"/>\n|-\n! December\n| {{flagicon|BEL}} [[Dodi Lukebakio]]\n| [[Fortuna D\u00fcsseldorf]]\n| {{flagicon|GER}} [[Jean Zimmer]]\n| Fortuna D\u00fcsseldorf\n| style=\"text-align:center\" | <ref name=\"bundesliga_19-2583-803\"/><ref name=\"rookie-award_2018-19\"/><ref name=\"bundesliga_2747-1210\"/>\n|-\n! January\n| {{flagicon|GER}} [[Leon Goretzka]]\n| [[FC Bayern Munich|Bayern Munich]]\n| {{fl